songs.title: Suicide Moshpit*
songs.lyrics:
Lyrics From Snippet

[Verse]
Flooded my wrist with ice
I got the first round like Mike
They leech and just suck me dry
Just like a parasite
I'm at the mountain view
They try to reach my height
My trap phone jumpin'
I don't need no satellite
We let the spot stake in
We had the club jump in-

[Chorus]
We ahead in the race, I do the dash
Know these haters tryna take my place, but they in last
Lil shorty think I'm up in the ways, I'm on her ass
Never settle down for second place, I'd rather pass
Suicide moshpit, I'm in the crowd with the fence
If my brother down bad, you know, I'm covering him in bands
